1.	The above results, reviewed by the Audit Committee, were approved by the Board of Directors at its Meeting held on 10th August, 2020.  The statutory auditors have carried out a "Limited Review" of financial results for the period ended 30th June, 2020. &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
2.	Segmental reporting as per Ind AS-108 issued by the ICAI is not applicable, as the Company is engaged in manufacture of a single line of product. &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
3.	The Company's production was stopped for 35 days during the quarter due to COVID-19 lock down imposed by Government of India.  The operations gradually resumed and attained normalcy thereafter.  Hence, financial results for the quarter have been adversely impacted. &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
4.	Figures for the previous periods have been regrouped, wherever necessary, to conform to the current period's classification. &lt;BR&gt; 
